<ansi fg="black-bold">.:</ansi> <ansi fg="magenta">Help for </ansi><ansi fg="command">mysticism</ansi>

<ansi fg="cyan">Mysticism</ansi> measures your connection to the magical forces of the world.
Those attuned to it can cast more spells and cast them more effectively.

<ansi fg="yellow">Mana</ansi>

* Each point of Mysticism adds <ansi fg="cyan">3 maximum MP</ansi>. Without mana you cannot
  cast spells, so this stat is essential for any spellcaster.
* Improves the rate at which your mana recovers between fights.

<ansi fg="yellow">Magic</ansi>

* Directly improves your spellcasting success, making it easier to land
  spells against resistant targets.
</ansi>
